.TH LEMONADE-INSTALL "1" "November 2025" "lemonade-install" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lemonade-install \- Installation utility for Lemonade LLM models and components
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lemonade-install
[\fI\,OPTIONS\/\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
lemonade-install is a utility for installing and managing Lemonade LLM
models, drivers, and related components. It automates the setup process
for optimal LLM serving performance.
.SH OPTIONS
Run \fBlemonade-install --help\fR for detailed usage information.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lemonade (1),
.BR lemonade-server (1)
.SH AUTHOR
Lemonade SDK developers
.SH REPORTING BUGS
Report bugs at: https://github.com/lemonade-sdk/lemonade/issues
